introduction:
# Places we have been 
 In this blog post, we want to take you on our trip to the Dakotas. It has been an excimting time for us, and we saw a myriad of wildlife. See the map below for the places we have been to on this trip
body:
## Let's look at some places 
 Within our trip to the Dakota's, we have visited 3 National Parks and 2 State Parks. They are listed in the map above and are the following parks: 
 1. Badlands National Park 
 2. Wind cave National Pak 
 3. Custer State Park 
 4. Black Hills State Park 
 5. Theodore Roosevelt National Park
